+      }
+    }
{code}
Instead of this - can you please change the function to
a) Only trim the diagnostics string size in case of a relaunch
b) Instead of removing a line and setting the limit to 10*1000, take the last 'n' characters in the string where 'n' is a config setting.

3)
{code}
+    } catch (IOException e) {
